data.description: Introducing this charming 3 bed 2 bath home in the serene countryside that's your own slice or rural paradise. As you pull up to the amble attached covered parking you will be greeted by the beautifully maintained trees and meticulously maintained landscaping. Inside the home you will have a split living set up with two bedrooms and a full bath to one side of the home. Nestled on its own side a master suit awaits you with a stand alone shower and a soaker tub, with dual vanities. The central living of the home you will find a large open flow kitchen that seamlessly flows into the living room with plenty of room for entertaining. In keeping up with the times  a new AC unit and Roof have been added. Schedule a viewing today and discover the allure of countryside living at its finest!
